  "body": "Running the beacon node with `--disable-dynamic-committee-subnets` causes a panic.\r\n\r\n### Has this worked before in a previous version?\r\n\r\nNo.\r\n\r\n## ðŸ”¬ Minimal Reproduction\r\n\r\n`beacon-chain --disable-dynamic-committee-subnets`\r\n\r\n## ðŸ”¥ Error\r\n\r\n```\r\npanic: /eth2/%x/beacon_attestation_0 is not mapped to any message in GossipTopicMappings\r\ngoroutine 245 [running]:\r\ngithub.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain/sync.(*Service).subscribe(0xc00000c1e0, 0xc00ce886a0, 0x1d, 0xc0006b6d20, 0xc0006b6d30, 0xc00ce886a0)\r\n        beacon-chain/sync/subscriber.go:97 +0x18b\r\ngithub.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain/sync.(*Service).registerSubscribers(0xc00000c1e0)\r\n        beacon-chain/sync/subscriber.go:77 +0x3a9\r\ngithub.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain/sync.(*Service).registerHandlers(0xc00000c1e0)\r\n        beacon-chain/sync/service.go:244 +0x3dd\r\ncreated by github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/beacon-chain/sync.NewRegularSync\r\n        beacon-chain/sync/service.go:140 +0x32c\r\n```",
